      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts through all gears without hesitation. While the exterior shows some minor paint chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use, the body is straight and free of major dents. Inside, the cabin is clean and all electronics, including the infotainment and climate control, are fully functional. This is a dependable vehicle that is ready for the road, requiring no immediate major repairs, though a buyer should expect the standard wear-and-tear associated with a pre-owned car of this age.",
