      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved and looked after. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for someone new to take the wheel. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend road trips\u2014come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
