      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 power plant. This high-revving straight-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain sends power through a factory M-Variable Lock limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a VANOS system overhaul to ensure structural and mechanical integrity. The suspension retains its factory-tuned balance with refreshed bushings and dampers, providing the tactile feedback expected of the E46 chassis. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the vehicle remains a mechanically sound and exceptional example of analog performance engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
